[normal]AFS0076[bold]Written evidence submitted by [bold]GMB Union[bold] 
[normal]GMB is the largest trade union for school support staff, representing over 100,000 school workers nationally, an ever increasing number of whom work in academies. GMB
[normal] members in schools are teaching assistants of every level, provide caretaking and school meals, and work in a range of other auxiliary and support functions.
